# These Makefiles are for cleo3:
#
#  - M.exe for making an executable
#  - M.library for making a library
#  - M.tail for the real meat, included by M.exe and M.library
#  - M.processor for making a shared processor
#
#  simply make a copy of either M.exe or M.library to your directory
#  which contains your library code and rename it "Makefile"
#
#  e.g.:
#
#  MyLibrary/
#            Makefile     (either M.exe or M.library!)
#            MyLibrary/   (contains header files)
#            Class/       (contains code)
#            Instantiate  (only necessary, if need explicit template 
#                          instantiation)
#            Test/        (optional for testing code)
#
#
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
#
# Author: Martin Lohner
# Date:   12/8/97
#
# $Id: README,v 1.2 1998/01/05 16:50:17 cleo3 Exp $
#
# $Log: README,v $
# Revision 1.2  1998/01/05 16:50:17  cleo3
# added M.processor for making shared processors
#
# Revision 1.1  1997/12/08 18:20:59  mkl
# sample Makefiles
#
#
